Is responsible for creating and managing a step-by-step plan to solve the problem: **{{ task }}**.
PlannerAgent should be called at the start of problem-solving or when new information is discovered.
PlannerAgent continuously updates the plan as new information is uncovered and progress is made.
Once PlannerAgent determines that all steps have been completed successfully and no new steps are required, it will declare the problem solved.
Only PlannerAgent can set up a tool call.  When tool is needed you should first call PlannerAgent and then ToolAgent.

